==Useful Info==
'''Black draconians''' are the [[electricity]]-themed members of the [[list of draconians|draconian]] family. Their lightning breath attacks deal more damage than any other draconian breath attack, especially if they manage to [[multizap]] you (though they may also do heavy damage to anything else nearby). They can be found primarily in [[the Realm of Zot]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Electricity resistance will greatly reduce the damage of their breath attacks. [[Freezing]] and [[dragon slaying]]-[[brand]]ed weapons help make combat against them much easier.
*Black draconians can [[fly]], so casters with [[Airstrike]] can kill them fairly easily. If there's a more immediate threat present, however, deal with that first.
